@startuml
title Pet Image Upload Sequence

actor "Catalog Manager" as Manager
participant "Feature Review Workspace" as Workspace
participant "Pet API" as PetAPI
database "Pet Catalog" as Catalog
collections "Image Storage" as Images

Manager -> Workspace: Select pet for image upload
' operationId: getPetById
Workspace -> PetAPI: GET /pet/{petId}
PetAPI -> Catalog: Verify Pet exists
PetAPI --> Workspace: Pet details

Manager -> Workspace: Upload binary image with metadata
' operationId: uploadFile
Workspace -> PetAPI: POST /pet/{petId}/uploadImage
PetAPI -> Images: Store image bytes
PetAPI --> Workspace: ApiResponse confirmation

Manager -> Workspace: Update pet visual metadata
' operationId: updatePet
Workspace -> PetAPI: PUT /pet
PetAPI -> Catalog: Save photo URL or related Pet fields
PetAPI --> Workspace: Updated Pet
@enduml
